import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data['time'] = pd.to_datetime(data['time'], format='%H:%M:%S', errors='coerce')
    data = data[pd.notna(data['time'])]
    data = data.sort_values(by='time')
    plt.plot(data['time'], data['count'], color='blue')
    plt.xlabel('Time')
    plt.ylabel('Count')
    plt.title('What is the trend of count over time?', wrap=True)
    return plt

chart = plot(data)
```

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data['time'] = pd.to_datetime(data['time'], format='%H:%M:%S', errors='coerce')
    data = data[pd.notna(data['time'])]
    data['hour'] = data['time'].dt.hour
    data = data.groupby('hour').mean().reset_index()
    fig, ax = plt.subplots()
    ax.bar(data['hour'], data['count'], color='blue')
    ax.axhline(y=data['count'].mean(), color='red', linestyle='--', label='Average Count')
    ax.legend()
    ax.set_xlabel('Hour')
    ax.set_ylabel('Count')
    ax.set_title('What is the average count per time period?')
    plt.xticks(data['hour'])
    plt.tight_layout()
    return plt

chart = plot(data)
```

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    plt.hist(data['count'], bins=20, color='blue', alpha=0.5)
    plt.axvline(data['count'].mean(), color='red', linestyle='dashed', linewidth=1, label='Mean')
    plt.axvline(data['count'].median(), color='green', linestyle='dashed', linewidth=1, label='Median')
    plt.xlabel('Count')
    plt.ylabel('Frequency')
    plt.title('What is the distribution of count?')
    plt.legend()
    return plt

chart = plot(data)
```

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd
import seaborn as sns

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data = data.dropna()
    fig, ax = plt.subplots(figsize=(8, 6))
    sns.boxplot(x=data['count'], ax=ax, color='skyblue')
    ax.set_title('What is the maximum and minimum count?')
    ax.axvline(data['count'].min(), color='red', linestyle='--', label=f'Minimum: {data["count"].min():.2f}')
    ax.axvline(data['count'].max(), color='green', linestyle='--', label=f'Maximum: {data["count"].max():.2f}')
    ax.legend()
    return plt

chart = plot(data)
